Package: philengine
Title: Text Quantification Engine Client for Phil Ecosystem
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Yusuke", "Matsui", email = "mail.to.matsui@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Client package for the Phil text quantification engine. Provides
    R interfaces for embedding texts using multiple backends (sentence-transformers,
    OpenAI, Cohere) via the philapi REST API, and for computing lexical, structural,
    and intertextual features of philosophical texts.
